<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:13:31 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>数据显示，中国比亚迪在新加坡和东南亚的电动汽车市场上扩大了对特斯拉的领先优势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</link><description>政府数据显示，今年上半年，中国比亚迪在新加坡扩大了对特斯拉的销量领先优势，凸显了这家全球最大电动汽车制造商在中国竞争对手销量方面面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>雷米首席财务官表示，尚未给出对中国白兰地调查做出决定的日期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</link><description>在顶级干邑生产商上周参加了有关该问题的听证会后，人头马君度首席财务官周三表示，北京方面尚未给出对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查做出决定的官方时间表。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯指责美国加剧北极紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</link><description>俄罗斯周三指责华盛顿加剧北极紧张局势，并驳斥了美国军方关于俄罗斯和中国在该地区加强合作可能影响地区稳定的说法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称与中国就争议浅滩的紧张局势拥有“共识”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</link><description>菲律宾一名高级安全官员周三表示，菲律宾和中国已就缓和南海有争议的浅滩的紧张局势达成共识，去年这里曾多次发生对抗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:35:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-has-common-understanding-with-china-tensions-disputed-shoal-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰最高外交官在广州会见中国王毅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</link><description>乌克兰最高外交官周三在广州与中国外交部长王毅举行了三个多小时的会谈，基辅称这是一次为期多日的访问，讨论如何在与俄罗斯的战争中实现“公平和平”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 07:25:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-top-diplomat-meets-chinas-wang-yi-talks-guangzhou-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国详细介绍了扩大国家机密的法律，着眼于数据安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国本周公布了修订后的《国家秘密法》的细节，该法改变了对政府官员处理机密信息的限制，禁止负责掌握国家秘密的人员未经批准出国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:40:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-details-expanded-law-state-secrets-eyeing-data-security-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>经历上半年疲软后，保时捷力图恢复生产并提高利润率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</link><description>保时捷表示，在供应链障碍、电动汽车需求放缓和中国销量下滑影响上半年业绩后，该公司正在努力恢复产量并重新确定支出优先顺序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/porsche-profits-drop-after-months-lower-sales-supply-chain-issues-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>东盟部长们在老挝举行会议，寻求解决缅甸危机和南海紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</link><description>东南亚集团东盟周三在老挝举行会议，寻求推进陷入僵局的解决缅甸危机和缓和南中国海紧张局势的努力，而几天后，世界各大国的高级外交官将齐聚一堂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-seeks-tackle-myanmar-crisis-south-china-sea-tension-ministers-meet-laos-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia因汽车需求低迷而下调前景，着眼于与中国汽车制造商进行交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-trims-2024-outlook-lower-auto-demand-extra-costs-north-america-2024-07-24/</link><description>按收入计算，全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周三下调了销售额和利润率预期，原因是全球汽车需求低迷以及与墨西哥汽车内饰业务供应商发生纠纷，导致其股价下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:35:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-trims-2024-outlook-lower-auto-demand-extra-costs-north-america-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾命令离岸博彩中心的外籍工人两个月内离开</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯决定取缔离岸赌博公司后，菲律宾移民局周三表示，该国已下令在离岸赌博公司工作的外国人在两个月内离开该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:25:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-orders-foreign-workers-offshore-gaming-hubs-leave-2-months-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：LGES 正在与中国材料公司洽谈为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</link><description>韩国 LG 能源解决方案公司 (LGES) 一位高管表示，正在与三个中国供应商就为欧洲生产低成本电动汽车电池进行谈判，欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税后，竞争将加剧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 05:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lg-energy-solution-talks-with-chinese-firms-make-low-cost-ev-batteries-europe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国量化基金在打击行动中遭受严重损失</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-quant-funds-suffer-deep-losses-amid-crackdown-2024-07-24/</link><description>数据显示，中国计算机驱动的“量化”对冲基金今年上半年遭受了严重损失，表现逊于国内传统股票策略和其他流行的全球基金策略。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:33:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/chinas-quant-funds-suffer-deep-losses-amid-crackdown-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>盈利报告疲弱，股市暴跌，日元创七周新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-24/</link><description>由于特斯拉、Alphabet 以及欧洲奢侈品牌的业绩令人失望，周三全球股市下跌，而日元在下周央行会议之前飙升至七周高点。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 02:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”逼近台湾加强，工作暂停，一人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-hunkers-down-ahead-arrival-typhoon-gaemi-2024-07-24/</link><description>周三，台湾因台风“高美”的到来而陷入困境，金融市场关闭，航班取消，造成一人死亡，而军队则在暴雨中待命。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 00:23:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-hunkers-down-ahead-arrival-typhoon-gaemi-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>独家：Nvidia 批准三星 HBM3 芯片用于中国市场处理器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，三星电子的第四代高带宽内存或 HBM3 芯片已首次获得 Nvidia 批准用于其处理器。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 23:03:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-clears-samsungs-hbm3-chips-use-china-market-processor-sources-say-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>